    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once caramelised, add <strong>half</strong> of your <strong>vegetable stock</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) to the pan, increase the heat to medium-high and cook until the stock has completely absorbed</p><p>Add the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>ground</strong> <strong>smoked paprika</strong> and stir well</p>",
