      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained linguine</strong> and the <strong>remaining vegetable stock</strong> to the pan, then cook until reduced and thickened</p><p>Once thickened, add the <strong>seasoned crème fraîche</strong> and stir to combine – this is your <strong>creamy mushroom stroganoff</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of the reserved starchy pasta water if the sauce is looking a little dry</p>",
